<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 16:08:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尼尔奥兹不是一场战斗，而是一场系统性的屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-wasnt-a-battle-it-was-a-systematic-massacre/0000018b-4cff-dc3c-a5df-dcff56030000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，以色列国防军首次允许记者进入以色列加沙边境的尼尔奥兹基布兹。这些是《国土报》摄影师 Moti Milrod 拍摄的照片</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 13:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-wasnt-a-battle-it-was-a-systematic-massacre/0000018b-4cff-dc3c-a5df-dcff56030000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡任命处理加沙以色列人质事件的人谴责欧洲特使支持奥斯陆协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/pms-appointee-on-hostages-yells-at-european-envoys-for-supporting-oslo-accords/0000018b-4c75-d5d2-afef-ccfdbcc80000</link><description>在一次讨论释放加沙人质的会议上，ret。双桅船。加尔·赫希 (Gal Hirsch) 将军对欧洲大使 30 年前针对以色列和巴勒斯坦人的政策大喊大叫。一位大使：“我们想提供帮助，不需要政治说教”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 12:22:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/pms-appointee-on-hostages-yells-at-european-envoys-for-supporting-oslo-accords/0000018b-4c75-d5d2-afef-ccfdbcc80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将面临的耻辱将远远大于他试图逃避的耻辱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/the-shame-that-will-follow-netanyahu-will-be-far-greater-than-one-he-attempted-to-escape/0000018b-4bc8-d1fd-a59f-efdb683d0000</link><description>比比作为“以色列保护者”的神话已经打破。 “一切都结束了，”执政联盟的一名高级成员本周表示。 “政府将无法幸存”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 07:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/the-shame-that-will-follow-netanyahu-will-be-far-greater-than-one-he-attempted-to-escape/0000018b-4bc8-d1fd-a59f-efdb683d0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫正式要求国会为以色列提供143亿美元的紧急安全援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-live/white-house-formally-asks-congress-for-14-3-billion-in-emergency-security-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4b06-d1fd-a59f-ef9ff9ed0000</link><description>随着紧张局势升级，以色列为黎巴嫩北部边境附近的居民制定疏散计划 ■ 以色列国防军表示，一夜之间袭击了加沙的 100 多个目标 ■ 拜登要求国会向以色列提供 140 亿美元的军事援助 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯： 3,200 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，约 11,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 05:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-live/white-house-formally-asks-congress-for-14-3-billion-in-emergency-security-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4b06-d1fd-a59f-ef9ff9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>导致哈马斯袭击的失败永远改变了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/underprepared-and-overconfident-israel-failed-to-spot-the-signs-of-impending-disaster/0000018b-4976-d03a-afcb-697edb020000</link><description>安全机构热衷于敌人被威慑的观念 ■ 内塔尼亚胡扶植哈马斯，而以色列人却视而不见 ■ 多年来忽视巴以冲突的后果，突然付出了沉重的代价</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 03:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/underprepared-and-overconfident-israel-failed-to-spot-the-signs-of-impending-disaster/0000018b-4976-d03a-afcb-697edb020000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡仍然相信他能够逃避指责并在以色列最大的灾难中幸存下来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-still-believes-he-can-dodge-blame-and-survive-israels-greatest-catastrophe/0000018b-496e-dc3c-a5df-ddeec2aa0000</link><description>加沙边境灾难发生两周后，总理甚至没有暗示要承担责任——与许多高级国防官员不同。与此同时，拜登动员到以色列一边可能会让他以后的事情变得复杂</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-still-believes-he-can-dodge-blame-and-survive-israels-greatest-catastrophe/0000018b-496e-dc3c-a5df-ddeec2aa0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登将向国会请求 140 亿美元的以色列军事援助：“敌对行为者将知道以色列比以往任何时候都更强大”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-ask-congress-for-unprecedented-14b-in-military-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4a84-d199-a7eb-dfde51e20000</link><description>在罕见的椭圆形办公室讲话中，美国总统将哈马斯与普京进行了比较，称“他们都想彻底消灭邻国的民主国家”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 00:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-ask-congress-for-unprecedented-14b-in-military-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4a84-d199-a7eb-dfde51e20000</guid></item><item><title>“俄罗斯轮盘赌”：以色列遭受轰炸最严重的城市的居民得不到保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</link><description>阿什凯隆是加沙战争中目标最严重的城市，该城的约 40,000 名居民缺乏适当的保护以免受火箭弹袭击——尽管事实上已经为此编列了资金预算</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 22:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们在达兰萨拉冥想。突然，来自以色列的电话开始涌入”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：在战争期间，一名年轻女子返回以色列的家，而另一名年轻女子则在拉脱维亚与家人团聚</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-49d3-d03a-afcb-69fb35f60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:27:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-49d3-d03a-afcb-69fb35f60000</guid></item><item><title>战时考验以色列的民主</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/testing-israels-democracy-in-wartime/0000018b-495e-d5d2-afef-cdffc47a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/testing-israels-democracy-in-wartime/0000018b-495e-d5d2-afef-cdffc47a0000</guid></item><item><title>睁大眼睛：以色列情报部门对哈马斯的军事集结视而不见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/eyes-wide-shut-israeli-intelligence-was-blind-to-hamas-military-build-up/0000018b-4906-d03a-afcb-693e52210000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:18:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/eyes-wide-shut-israeli-intelligence-was-blind-to-hamas-military-build-up/0000018b-4906-d03a-afcb-693e52210000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯对抗更强大的以色列的长期目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-long-term-goals-in-its-fight-against-a-stronger-israel/0000018b-493f-d5d2-afef-cdff422d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-long-term-goals-in-its-fight-against-a-stronger-israel/0000018b-493f-d5d2-afef-cdff422d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯真的像伊斯兰国吗？专家讲解</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-hamas-really-like-isis-experts-explain/0000018b-493f-d1fd-a59f-edbfbe090000</link><description>是否有可能与哈马斯合作？十二位研究伊斯兰团体及其历史的学者努力确定它是如何成为今天的怪物的，并提出了行动方案</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 20:57:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-hamas-really-like-isis-experts-explain/0000018b-493f-d1fd-a59f-edbfbe090000</guid></item><item><title>武装警卫保护本周末在美国校园参加安息日活动的犹太学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/armed-guards-to-protect-jewish-students-attending-shabbat-events-on-u-s-campuses/0000018b-4996-d1fd-a59f-ed9f70eb0000</link><description>希勒尔国际总裁表示，我们需要对真正的威胁保持警惕。在针对加沙战争的一波反以色列集会之后，犹太学生组织正在向大学施压，要求其加强安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 20:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/armed-guards-to-protect-jewish-students-attending-shabbat-events-on-u-s-campuses/0000018b-4996-d1fd-a59f-ed9f70eb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯袭击后失踪的一些人将无法找到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</link><description>根据以色列军队的最新数据，有 100 至 200 人被列为失踪人员，随着尸体身份的确认，这一数字预计会发生变化。据军方了解，约有 30 名 16 岁以下儿童被绑架</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:57:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正式加入美国免签证计划，立即生效</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</link><description>以色列入境原定于 11 月 30 日开始，但由于哈马斯袭击后美国驻以色列大使馆暂停签证处理，迫于国会压力，这一进程已加快。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:41:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</guid></item><item><title>2007年的内塔尼亚胡：总理对国家安全负有个人责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</link><description>“在像以色列这样的国家，如果一个人不具备某种塑造外交安全概念的能力，你就不能任命他为总理，因为如果是这样，那么这些机构就真正具有统治力；内塔尼亚胡向一个正在调查 2006 年第二次黎巴嫩战争的委员会作证说：“他不控制这些机构，也不指导它们”</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 18:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人没有安全的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</link><description>以色列最伟大的成就之一是它为本国公民以及世界各地的犹太人提供的安全和繁荣，让他们偶尔忘记自己面临着犹太人的仇恨。从以色列南部到澳大利亚悉尼，情况已不再如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 17:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在安曼举行的中东峰会可能已取消，但美国仍应采取严肃的外交行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</link><description>拜登等美国总统周三的访问可能会成为中东外交的一个重大转折点，但问题是这是否是白宫想要的</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 16:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</guid></item></channel></rss>